song.title: Rotagilla
song.info:
FM + PCM samples in ScreamTracker 3. Use ST3, Schism Tracker or any other software that can play S3M files with adlib patches. Also watch the [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-lFNYJ7B820]video[/url] of the tune playing in ST3.
Track 10 from Ubiktune's 11th release, "Autumntunes". Download link here: http://ubiktune.org/releases/ubi011/
